race.comment: ALPHA BRAVO (1) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this calibre. Tuned up for this with two recent trials and can run a big race while fresh. CORRUPTED (7) has been right there in all four runs this campaign and looks to be working up to another victory. Sure to play a major role. THE HAMO (3) resumed with a solid win over this course and distance and will have taken some confidence from that first-up victory. Rates among the leading hopes. KICKATINALONG (8) is yet to miss a drum in three fresh appearances and is worth plenty of thought first-up. CAPITAL DIVA (10) goes well for jockey Lerena who has two wins from as many steers. Makes plenty of appeal.
